# Trips UI (PR #25 branch work)

Branch: `feat/trip-add-app-bar-action`. Do not regress these patterns when editing Trips.

## Segment control (`trip_phase_segment.dart`, `trip_phase_style.dart`)
- **Active** tab only: live ripple rings + pulsing dot when selected. No ripple on trip cards.
- Phase colors: Active = orange, **Upcoming = light blue** (`#F0F9FF` / `#0369A1`), Done = grey.

## New Trip sheet (`create_trip_bottom_sheet.dart`)
- Opened from app bar **+** (no FAB). No sheet title/subtitle; drag handle is **inside** `SheetScaffold`.
- `showCloseButton: false` — dismiss via swipe-down or after slide-to-create.
- `showModalBottomSheet`: `showDragHandle: false`, `useRootNavigator: true`.
- **Must** wrap sheet with `BlocProvider.value(value: tripListBloc)` — root navigator sheet is outside page `BlocProvider`.
- Form: hero **New Trip Name**, location pin (not emoji) for destination, From/To dates, minimal currency row, people icon on buddies.
- Submit: `SwipeToConfirm` label **"Slide to create trip"** — not a `FilledButton`.

## Slide-to-create (`swipe_to_confirm.dart`)
- Spring snap, white thumb + chevrons, teal fill. Fire `onConfirmed` immediately on complete.
- Dismiss: `Navigator.of(context, rootNavigator: true).pop(true)`.

## Trip list bloc (`trip_list_bloc.dart`)
- `_createdTrips` persists user-created trips across `TripListLoadRequested` (mock reload must not wipe them).

## Currency (`currency_options.dart`)
- Horizontal scroll chips: **flag + symbol** only (e.g. 🇯🇵 ¥). No country name on chips.

## Date picker (`trip_date_picker_sheet.dart`)
- Use `TripDatePickerSheet.show` — **not** `showDatePicker`.
- Bottom sheet: flight icons, teal preview, month grid, tap-to-select.
- Return mode: duration shortcuts `3d` `5d` `7d` `10d` `14d`; `minDate` = departure when picking end.

## Sheet scaffold (`sheet_scaffold.dart`)
- `title` optional (omit for create trip). `showDragHandle` renders handle inside sheet body.

## Add Spot sheet (`add_spot_bottom_sheet.dart`)
- Same chrome as create trip: no title, `showCloseButton: false`, drag handle inside `SheetScaffold`.
- `showModalBottomSheet`: `showDragHandle: false`, `useRootNavigator: true`.
- **Must** wrap with `BlocProvider.value(value: tripDetailBloc)` — root navigator sheet is outside page `BlocProvider`.
- Form: hero **Spot name**, location pin for address, emoji-only category chips, soft card for hours / duration / notes.
- Shared primitives live in `sheet_form_primitives.dart` (`SheetHeroField`, `SheetSoftCard`, `SheetSectionHeader`, etc.).
- Submit: `SwipeToConfirm` label **"Slide to add spot"** — not a `FilledButton`.
- Dismiss: `Navigator.of(context, rootNavigator: true).pop()` after brief success beat.
